project: Welcome, adventurer. Peace has been gone from this land for a long time, ever since Atlantis' king became greedy. The King made life miserable for everyone, including you. He murdered your family and took everything you had. Now you must have your revenge and restore balance to the world.

Instructions
Go through the ocean to earn coins to gear up.
Get coins by defeating sharks.
Enter the portal in each area to advance through 3 sea levels and reach Atlantis.
Return to the surface in the Pause menu.
Dying -> surface, losing everything.

Controls
Move: WASD / Arrow keys
Shoot: Space
Interact: E
Pause: P
